Description of files in this directory:

run-benchmark     -- The main script for running a benchmark. It tries to compile the benchmark and if the compilation was successful, tries to run the benchmark. In case of errors, it calls ./generate-report to generate some report about the error. Can take some command-line parameters (see the script).

generate-report   -- Generates some reports about compiling-time and runtime errors.

update-and-make   -- Calls ./cvs-update-all and ./remake-everything.

cvs-update-all    -- cvs updates the entire FLEX.

remake-everything -- remakes everything in Code, Runtime and Realtime directories of FLEX.

clean             -- removes temporary files after running all tasks

temp              -- a directory for keeping some temporary files needed for compiling and running tasks

results           -- a directory for keeping some results
